headline: Is Williams-Sonoma Still Attractive After Its Huge Multi Year Share Price Rally in 2025?
summary: Wondering if Williams-Sonoma at around $190 a share is still attractive after its huge run, or if most of the easy money has already been made? Think of this as a clear headed look at whether the current price matches the underlying value. The stock has climbed 1.8% over the last week and 9.3% in the past month, adding to a powerful 236.4% gain over three years and 290.0% over five years. Those kinds of returns tend to change both investors expectations and risk appetite. Recent headlines...
